      • extractDocumentaryUnit

        protected Map<String,Object> extractDocumentaryUnit(Map<String,Object> itemData)
                                             throws ValidationError
        Extract DocumentaryUnit properties from the itemData and return them as a new Map. This implementation only extracts the objectIdentifier.

        This implementation does not throw ValidationErrors.

        Parameters:
        itemData - a Map containing raw properties of a DocumentaryUnit
        Returns:
        a new Map containing the objectIdentifier property
        Throws:
        ValidationError - never

      • extractUnknownProperties
